Package gridsim.parallel.profile

Interface Summary
PartitionPredicate This interface is used to filter what jobs/reservations should be put in a given partition by policies that use multiple partitions or queues.
ScheduleItem ScheduleItem represents an item that can be put in a scheduling queue.
 

Class Summary
LinkedTreeMap<K,V> Red-Black tree based implementation of the SortedMap interface.
LinkedTreeMap.Entry<K,V> Node in the Tree.
PartProfile This class represents the profile containing the ranges of PEs available at given simulation times.
PartProfileEntry The PartProfileEntry class represents an entry in the availability profile.
PERange This class represents a range of PEs.
PERangeList This class represents a list of PERange's.
Profile This class represents the profile containing the ranges of PEs available at given simulation times.
ProfileEntry The ProfileEntry class represents an entry in the availability profile.
ResourcePartition This class represents a resource partition for a multiple-partition based availability profile.
SingleProfile This class represents the profile containing the ranges of PEs available at given simulation times.
SingleProfileEntry The SingleProfileEntry class represents an entry in the availability profile.
TimeSlot This class defines a time slot.
